151
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,600
That's too sappy.

152
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:55,200
On your first day taking over, you're already destroying your own reputation.

153
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,659
You're really something.

154
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,960
I'm destroying the old, foolish Song Qiyue.

155
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:04,090
The new store opens tomorrow morning.

156
