Yangshan Cottage.

161
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,240
That doesn't sound very good.

162
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,440
Think of another one.

163
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:25,440
How about 'Peach Blossom Spring Cottage'?

164
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,440
That sounds nice.

165
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,100
Let's call it 'Dream Dwelling' then.

166
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:29,880
Go to sleep.

167
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,900
Are you always this casual about naming things?

168
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,960
