171
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:56,120
Whether locals or tourists,

172
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:58,000
everyone comes here to pray for blessings.

173
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,720
The final step before opening the guesthouse

174
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,320
