182
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,360
About you guaranteeing for me,

183
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,690
I won't let you lose out.

184
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,840
I'll give you ten percent of the guesthouse's share.

185
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:24,400
Now we're in the same boat.

186
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:27,760
So your belief counts too.

